•the inability to successfully combine the businesses of BigBear.ai and Pangiam in a manner that permits the combined company to achieve the anticipated benefits from the Pangiam Acquisition, which would result in those benefits not being realized partly or wholly in the time frame currently anticipated or at all;
•creation of uniform standards, controls, procedures, policies and information systems; and
•potential unknown liabilities and unforeseen increased expenses.
